replies.body:
Hey Frosted o/
Favourite holiday food? Dutch food. 
Dark chocolate or milk chocolate? Milk for sure, I really can't stand dark.
Thoughts on me? ;) Very friendly and approachable mod. People can easily approach you with any concerns they have, which is great to see.
Best song you've listened to in the past week? Stay by Kygo 

@Tazz - Opinions on me - You're a great Official and CSGO player, however I have to question the way you're running League. Other than that, very funny guy, who's extremely chill.

@Budah - Avicus rn seems to be improving with the likes of voting, planned updates and full 1.8. I can only say that it's a step in the right direction. The staff team seems great rn, lot's of new faces on the Junior team. I hope to see them do well on their trials. You're a great friend, very chill and funny. Without you I would have left ages ago.
